{{Infobox dungeon |name = Pokémon Mansion |image = [[File:Pokemon Mansion.png|350px]] |caption = An overhead map of the Pokémon Mansion. |tokens = 1,500 |location = West of Cinnabar Island. }} The '''Pokémon Mansion''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kanto]]. It has 25 tiles arranged in a 5x5 square, including 5 chest tiles, 13 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
